snippet.title: Keio Yuugekitai 2 (Saturn) - Japanese TV Commercial
snippet.description: Here is a Japanese TV Commercial for Keio Yuugekitai Katsugekihen for the Sega Saturn. The game was released in PAL regions as Keio Flying Squadron 2...
